<HEADLINE>
<P>
NOT OUT OF WOODS YET WITH TIGER ON PROWL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 After watching Tiger Woods winning the U.S. Amateur golf tournament, I think 
the professional golfers should take up a collection to pay his college 
expenses for four years and keep him off the PGA Tour. 
