<P>
WORLD IN BRIEF; SYRIA; PEACE TALKS PAVE WAY FOR CHRISTOPHER VISIT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Presidents Hafez Assad of Syria and Elias Hrawi of Lebanon met to discuss the 
Middle East peace process in preparation for Secretary of State Warren 
Christopher's visit to the region this month.Christopher is trying to revive 
