<P>
 The leader of an Islamic sect outlawed by Malaysia's government as a security 
threat was sent back to Malaysia by Thai authorities, police said.Officials in 
Thailand said Ashaari Mohamad was detained as an illegal immigrant after the 
Malaysian government notified them that his passport had been revoked. He was 
