<TEXT>
<P>
 Cook, Rolland H., 78, of Lancaster, retired aerospace foreman. Halley-Olsen 
Funeral Chapel, Lancaster.  
</P>
<P>
 Cruz, Rachel Marie, 90, of San Fernando, homemaker.Noble Chapel, San Fernando. 
 
