</P>
<P>
 Leveski , Geraldine M., 71, of Palmdale, retired certified nursing assistant 
for Shea Convalescent Home. Halley-Olsen Funeral Chapel, Palmdale.  
</P>
<P>
 Marrone, Sam Selvedore, 70, of Van Nuys, retired real estate agent. 
Utter-McKinley Mortuary, Mission Hills.  
</P>
<P>
 Marsh, Thelma Isabelle, 79, of Los Angeles, formerly of Chatsworth, homemaker. 
J.T. Oswald Mortuary, Reseda.  
</P>
<P>
 Palm, Thelma Lee, 77, of Sylmar, homemaker. San Fernando Mortuary, San 
Fernando.  
</P>
<P>
 Ramos, Santos S., 78, of Pacoima, retired construction laborer. Utter-McKinley 
Mortuary, Mission Hills.  
</P>
<P>
 Smith, Verna P., 82, of Encino, homemaker. Praiswater Funeral Home, Van Nuys.  
</P>
<P>
 Spence, Edward Vincent, 74, of Sun Valley, carpenter for Rolls-Russell Co. San 
Fernando Mortuary, San Fernando.  
</P>
<P>
