<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA090394-0208 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 075749 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 3, 1994, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
