Jose State (2-9) 13-46, Cal Fresno State 7. Temple (1-10) 0-62, Rutgers Akron 
8. Stanford (4-7) 17-46, Cal N'western 9. Chapman (0-0) Idle Whittier 10. East 
Carolina (2-9) 0-35, Washington Duke 11. Wide Awake Forest (2-9); 12. Arkansas 
State (2-8-1); 13. Ole Southern Miss (2-8-10); 14. Maryland (2-9); 15. 
