 El Dorado -- Five returning starters on the offensive line. 
</P>
<P>
 Foothill -- Lots of size and a burner in Trammel Robinson. 
</P>
<P>
 Fullerton -- Loaded with 20 returning starters 
</P>
<P>
 Los Amigos -- Quarterback Ape Tuato is a load. 
</P>
