</P>
<P>
 Servite -- Should dominate the new Golden West League. 
</P>
<P>
 Troy -- Someone has to win the Freeway League. 
</P>
<P>
 Valencia -- Always good, even in down years like this one. 
</P>
<P>
 Woodbridge -- Ian Dominelli is brutal on defense.  
